                    "value": "<p>The infernal tide conjures murky water to fill the lungs of all creatures that can't breathe water within a @Template[type:cone|distance:30]. Each target in the area must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:30] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target coughs up water and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target must hold its breath. The only action it can take is to attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:30] save to expel the water, which is a single action.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target falls @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Unconscious] and begins suffocating. If the target succeeds at its Fortitude save while suffocating, it coughs up the water and can breathe again.</p>"
                },
